"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ourPrivacy notice\", \"from\": 424, \"to\": 441}, {\"ngram\": \"A key hunting strategy\", \"from\": 442, \"to\": 464}, {\"ngram\": \"ancient human ancestors\", \"from\": 474, \"to\": 497}, {\"ngram\": \"modern athletes\", \"from\": 506, \"to\": 521}, {\"ngram\": \"long distances\", \"from\": 539, \"to\": 553}, {\"ngram\": \"a new study\", \"from\": 568, \"to\": 579}, {\"ngram\": \"the ParisOlympicsmarathon\", \"from\": 599, \"to\": 624}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While humans are not the best sprinters in the animal kingdom, they are excellent atendurance running.\", \"from\": 628, \"to\": 730, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"humans\", \"from\": 634, \"to\": 640}, {\"ngram\": \"the best sprinters\", \"from\": 649, \"to\": 667}, {\"ngram\": \"the animal kingdom\", \"from\": 671, \"to\": 689}, {\"ngram\": \"excellent atendurance\", \"from\": 700, \"to\": 721}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our running muscles are dominated by slow-twitch, fatigue-resistant fibres with the ability tosweat and dissipate heat.This enables us to run steadily for long distances even in hot weather.\", \"from\": 732, \"to\": 922, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our running muscles\", \"from\": 732, \"to\": 751}, {\"ngram\": \"slow-twitch, fatigue-resistant fibres\", \"from\": 769, \"to\": 806}, {\"ngram\": \"the ability tosweat\", \"from\": 812, \"to\": 831}, {\"ngram\": \"heat\", \"from\": 846, \"to\": 850}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 864, \"to\": 866}, {\"ngram\": \"long distances\", \"from\": 887, \"to\": 901}, {\"ngram\": \"hot weather\", \"from\": 910, \"to\": 921}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Traits enabling endurance running appeared in our ancestors some two million years ago, previous research shows, and \\\"may have been instrumental\\\" in the evolution of our body form.\", \"from\": 924, \"to\": 1104, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Traits enabling endurance\", \"from\": 924, \"to\": 949}, {\"ngram\": \"our ancestors\", \"from\": 970, \"to\": 983}, {\"ngram\": \"the evolution\", \"from\": 1073, \"to\": 1086}, {\"ngram\": \"our body form\", \"from\": 1090, \"to\": 1103}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These traits enabled hunters torelentlessly pursueprey until it was overcome by exhaustion.\", \"from\": 1105, \"to\": 1196, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These traits\", \"from\": 1105, \"to\": 1117}, {\"ngram\": \"hunters\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1133}, {\"ngram\": \"exhaustion\", \"from\": 1185, \"to\": 1195}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the latest study, researchers assessed around 400 descriptions of hunts dating from 1527AD through the early 20th century from 272 places across the world.\", \"from\": 1198, \"to\": 1356, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the latest study\", \"from\": 1201, \"to\": 1217}, {\"ngram\": \"researchers\", \"from\": 1219, \"to\": 1230}, {\"ngram\": \"around 400 descriptions\", \"from\": 1240, \"to\": 1263}, {\"ngram\": \"hunts\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1272}, {\"ngram\": \"1527AD\", \"from\": 1285, \"to\": 1291}, {\"ngram\": \"the early 20th century\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1322}, {\"ngram\": \"272 places\", \"from\": 1328, \"to\": 1338}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1346, \"to\": 1355}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They found that chasing prey to exhaustion was one of the most successful tactics, especially in hot weather and snowy conditions.\", \"from\": 1358, \"to\": 1488, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"prey\", \"from\": 1382, \"to\": 1386}, {\"ngram\": \"exhaustion\", \"from\": 1390, \"to\": 1400}, {\"ngram\": \"the most successful tactics\", \"from\": 1412, \"to\": 1439}, {\"ngram\": \"hot weather\", \"from\": 1455, \"to\": 1466}, {\"ngram\": \"snowy conditions\", \"from\": 1471, \"to\": 1487}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They also found cases of hunting teams employing social tactics.\", \"from\": 1489, \"to\": 1553, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"cases\", \"from\": 1505, \"to\": 1510}, {\"ngram\": \"teams\", \"from\": 1522, \"to\": 1527}, {\"ngram\": \"social tactics\", \"from\": 1538, \"to\": 1552}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We also have cases where there is an individual who will climb a hill nearby and use hand signals to indicate where the animal is going, so the person following can take shortcuts and save energy,\\\" Bruce Winterhalder, study co-author from the University of California Davis, said.\", \"from\": 1555, \"to\": 1836, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"cases\", \"from\": 1569, \"to\": 1574}, {\"ngram\": \"an individual\", \"from\": 1590, \"to\": 1603}, {\"ngram\": \"a hill\", \"from\": 1619, \"to\": 1625}, {\"ngram\": \"hand signals\", \"from\": 1641, \"to\": 1653}, {\"ngram\": \"the animal\", \"from\": 1672, \"to\": 1682}, {\"ngram\": \"the person\", \"from\": 1696, \"to\": 1706}, {\"ngram\": \"shortcuts\", \"from\": 1726, \"to\": 1735}, {\"ngram\": \"energy\", \"from\": 1745, \"to\": 1751}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\" Bruce Winterhalder\", \"from\": 1752, \"to\": 1772}, {\"ngram\": \"study co\", \"from\": 1774, \"to\": 1782}, {\"ngram\": \"author\", \"from\": 1783, \"to\": 1789}, {\"ngram\": \"the University\", \"from\": 1795, \"to\": 1809}, {\"ngram\": \"California Davis\", \"from\": 1813, \"to\": 1829}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For early humans who did not yet have ballistic weaponry like bows and arrows, endurance hunting brought significant advantages, researchers said.\", \"from\": 1838, \"to\": 1984, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"early humans\", \"from\": 1842, \"to\": 1854}, {\"ngram\": \"ballistic weaponry\", \"from\": 1876, \"to\": 1894}, {\"ngram\": \"bows\", \"from\": 1900, \"to\": 1904}, {\"ngram\": \"arrows\", \"from\": 1909, \"to\": 1915}, {\"ngram\": \"endurance hunting\", \"from\": 1917, \"to\": 1934}, {\"ngram\": \"significant advantages\", \"from\": 1943, \"to\": 1965}, {\"ngram\": \"researchers\", \"from\": 1967, \"to\": 1978}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Showing tactical athletic prowess was also a way to elevate their social status and chances of finding mates.\", \"from\": 1986, \"to\": 2095, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"tactical athletic prowess\", \"from\": 1994, \"to\": 2019}, {\"ngram\": \"a way\", \"from\": 2029, \"to\": 2034}, {\"ngram\": \"their social status\", \"from\": 2046, \"to\": 2065}, {\"ngram\": \"finding mates\", \"from\": 2081, \"to\": 2094}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Scientists said further research could help reveal more about the origins of the human running gait and the satisfying feeling of \\\"runner's high\\\".\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2243, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Scientists\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2107}, {\"ngram\": \"further research\", \"from\": 2113, \"to\": 2129}, {\"ngram\": \"the origins\", \"from\": 2159, \"to\": 2170}, {\"ngram\": \"the human running gait\", \"from\": 2174, \"to\": 2196}, {\"ngram\": \"the satisfying feeling\", \"from\": 2201, \"to\": 2223}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To run long distances, to have an evolved gait that's uniquely imbued with stamina is unusual in the animal world.\", \"from\": 2245, \"to\": 2360, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"long distances\", \"from\": 2253, \"to\": 2267}, {\"ngram\": \"an evolved gait\", \"from\": 2277, \"to\": 2292}, {\"ngram\": \"stamina\", \"from\": 2321, \"to\": 2328}, {\"ngram\": \"the animal world\", \"from\": 2343, \"to\": 2359}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If that inspires you to go for a run, great,\\\" Dr Winterhalder said.\", \"from\": 2361, \"to\": 2428, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a run\", \"from\": 2392, \"to\": 2397}, {\"ngram\": \"Dr Winterhalder\", \"from\": 2407, \"to\": 2422}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 2024 Paris Olympics could push this human ability further with what is touted to be the most gruelling marathon track ever.\", \"from\": 2430, \"to\": 2557, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 2024 Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 2430, \"to\": 2453}, {\"ngram\": \"this human ability\", \"from\": 2465, \"to\": 2483}, {\"ngram\": \"the most gruelling marathon track\", \"from\": 2518, \"to\": 2551}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The marathon, unlike at some of the recent Olympics, does not have a circuit of repeated loops.\", \"from\": 2559, \"to\": 2654, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The marathon\", \"from\": 2559, \"to\": 2571}, {\"ngram\": \"the recent Olympics\", \"from\": 2591, \"to\": 2610}, {\"ngram\": \"a circuit\", \"from\": 2626, \"to\": 2635}, {\"ngram\": \"repeated loops\", \"from\": 2639, \"to\": 2653}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is a full loop instead from Paris down to Versailles outside of the city, with three uphill stretches that are very steep and long.\", \"from\": 2655, \"to\": 2792, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2689, \"end\": 2694, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999976287416222, \"rank\": 2.371263942738108e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a full loop\", \"from\": 2664, \"to\": 2675}, {\"ngram\": \"Versailles\", \"from\": 2703, \"to\": 2713}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 2725, \"to\": 2733}, {\"ngram\": \"three uphill stretches\", \"from\": 2740, \"to\": 2762}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The course follows a historical path taken by thousands of marching men and women in October 1789 that made King Louis XVI ratify the Universal Declaration of the Rights of Man and Citizens.\", \"from\": 2794, \"to\": 2984, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2907, \"end\": 2916, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_XVI\", \"score\": 0.9999767898633889, \"rank\": 2.320735787133074e-05, \"text\": \"Louis XVI\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_XVI\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_XVI\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The course\", \"from\": 279